---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - VersetVie">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-primary)] to-[var(--color-secondary)] bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Privacy Policy
        </span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-tertiary)] italic mb-8">
        Last updated: October 17, 2025<br/>
        Version: 1.0
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-4">
            Welcome to <strong>VersetVie</strong>! We place great importance on protecting your personal data and being transparent about how we use it.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-4">
            This privacy policy explains:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] ml-4 mb-4">
            <li>What data we collect</li>
            <li>How we use it</li>
            <li>How we protect it</li>
            <li>What your rights are</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            By using VersetVie, you accept the practices described in this policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Data Collected</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">1.1 Data you provide to us</h3>
              <p class="mb-3">When using the application, we collect the following information <strong>only with your consent</strong>:</p>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Data stored locally on your device:</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li><strong>First name</strong>: Used to personalize your daily encouragements</li>
                <li><strong>Gender</strong> (Male/Female): Allows adaptation of encouragement wording</li>
                <li><strong>Email</strong> (100% optional): Only if you choose to provide it during onboarding. Used to send you important news about the app. You can use the app completely without email.</li>
                <li><strong>Usage preferences</strong>: Visual theme, animation speed, haptic feedback, text size, daily notification time</li>
              </ul>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Anonymized collected data:</h4>
              <p class="mb-2 text-sm">(sent to Supabase with an anonymous identifier)</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Age range</strong>: Used for anonymized statistics</li>
                <li><strong>Christian denomination</strong>: Helps understand our audience (sensitive data Article 9 GDPR - collected with your explicit consent)</li>
                <li><strong>Support choice</strong>: Free or active support</li>
                <li><strong>Notification preferences</strong>: Chosen period and time</li>
                <li>This data is linked to an <strong>anonymous identifier</strong> (analytics_user_id), not your real identity</li>
              </ul>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Optional publicly shared data:</h4>
              <p class="mb-2 text-sm">(with your explicit consent)</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Prayer intention</strong>: If you choose to share it on the community prayer wall, your first name and prayer will be visible to other users</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">1.2 Automatically collected data</h3>
              <p class="mb-3">To improve the application and understand how it's used, we automatically collect certain <strong>anonymous</strong> data:</p>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">Usage data (via Mixpanel - EU servers):</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>Interaction events (app opening, verse viewing, etc.)</li>
                <li>Usage statistics (number of verses viewed, streaks, etc.)</li>
                <li>Device type and operating system version</li>
                <li>Application version</li>
              </ul>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Attribution data (via Tenjin - only with ATT consent):</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>Application installation source</li>
                <li>Ad interactions (if you accepted ATT tracking on iOS)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">1.3 Data we do NOT collect</h3>
              <p class="mb-2">We <strong>NEVER</strong> collect the following data:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>‚ùå Email address (unless you choose to provide it during onboarding)</li>
                <li>‚ùå Phone number</li>
                <li>‚ùå Postal address</li>
                <li>‚ùå Precise geographic location</li>
                <li>‚ùå Banking or payment information (handled directly by Apple/Google)</li>
                <li>‚ùå Contacts or photos from your device</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Data Usage</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">2.1 Purposes</h3>
              <p class="mb-2">We use your data only for the following purposes:</p>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Experience personalization:</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>Display your first name in encouragements</li>
                <li>Adapt encouragement wording (masculine/feminine)</li>
                <li>Apply your display preferences (theme, text size, etc.)</li>
              </ul>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Application improvement:</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>Understand how the application is used (anonymous analytics)</li>
                <li>Identify bugs and technical issues</li>
                <li>Develop new features</li>
              </ul>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Communication with you:</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>Sending daily notifications (only if you've enabled this option)</li>
                <li>Reminder to discover your encouragement of the day</li>
              </ul>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Advertising attribution (only with your consent):</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>Measure the effectiveness of our advertising campaigns</li>
                <li>Understand how users discover the application</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">2.2 Legal basis (GDPR)</h3>
              <p class="mb-2">The processing of your data is based on the following legal grounds:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Consent</strong>: You explicitly accept our terms of use and this policy during onboarding</li>
                <li><strong>Contract execution</strong>: Necessary to provide you with the application's features</li>
                <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong>: Application improvement and anonymous audience measurement</li>
                <li><strong>Explicit consent (Article 9 GDPR)</strong>: For sensitive data concerning your religious beliefs (Christian denomination, shared prayers), we obtain your explicit consent during onboarding. You can withdraw this consent at any time by deleting your data via the application settings</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Data Storage and Security</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">3.1 Where is your data stored?</h3>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Local storage (on your device):</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>Your first name, gender, and preferences are stored <strong>locally</strong> on your device via AsyncStorage</li>
                <li>This data <strong>never leaves your device</strong></li>
                <li>It is deleted if you uninstall the application</li>
              </ul>

              <h4 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2 mt-3">Server storage (anonymous data only):</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Mixpanel</strong> (servers in the European Union üá™üá∫): Anonymous analytics</li>
                <li><strong>Tenjin</strong> (with ATT consent): Marketing attribution and advertising</li>
                <li><strong>RevenueCat</strong>: Subscription management (no personal data, only subscription information)</li>
                <li><strong>Supabase</strong> (European Union üá™üá∫): Community data (prayer wall, feedback, anonymized onboarding data)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">3.2 Security</h3>
              <p class="mb-2">We take the security of your data very seriously:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>‚úÖ Encrypted communications (HTTPS only)</li>
                <li>‚úÖ Local data protected by the operating system (iOS/Android)</li>
                <li>‚úÖ No personally identifiable data sent to our servers</li>
                <li>‚úÖ Mixpanel servers located in the EU (GDPR compliant)</li>
                <li>‚úÖ No data sharing with unauthorized third parties</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 4 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Data Sharing with Third Parties</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">4.1 Third-party services used</h3>

              <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm mt-3">
                  <thead>
                    <tr class="bg-[var(--color-background)]">
                      <th class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2 text-left">Service</th>
                      <th class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2 text-left">Purpose</th>
                      <th class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2 text-left">Data shared</th>
                      <th class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2 text-left">Location</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2"><strong>Mixpanel</strong></td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Anonymous analytics</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Usage events, anonymous user ID</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">üá™üá∫ European Union</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2"><strong>Tenjin</strong></td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Marketing attribution (with ATT consent)</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Device ID (IDFA/GAID), attribution events</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">International</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2"><strong>RevenueCat</strong></td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Subscription management</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Subscription information (no personal data)</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">United States üá∫üá∏</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2"><strong>Supabase</strong></td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Community data (prayer wall, feedback, anonymized onboarding data)</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">First name, gender, age range, denomination, email (optional), prayers (optional), feedback, support choice - linked to anonymous ID</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">üá™üá∫ European Union</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2"><strong>Apple App Store</strong></td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">iOS payments</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Billing information (managed by Apple)</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">International</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2"><strong>Google Play</strong></td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Android payments</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">Billing information (managed by Google)</td>
                      <td class="border border-[var(--color-border)] p-2">International</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">4.2 Guarantees</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>We <strong>never</strong> sell your data to third parties</li>
                <li>We only share your data with <strong>essential</strong> services for the application's operation</li>
                <li>These services are subject to contractual data protection obligations</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 5 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <p>Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the following rights:</p>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">5.1 Right of access</h3>
              <p class="mb-2">You can view all your data at any time in the application:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>Profile > My Information: First name, gender</li>
                <li>Profile > Settings: Display preferences</li>
                <li>Profile > Statistics: Usage data</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">5.2 Right to rectification</h3>
              <p>You can modify your information at any time: <strong>Profile > My Information > Edit</strong></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">5.3 Right to erasure</h3>
              <p class="mb-2">You can delete all your local data: <strong>Profile > Settings > Privacy > Delete all my data</strong></p>
              <p class="mb-2"><strong>Important</strong>: This action is irreversible and deletes all your local data (favorites, statistics, preferences).</p>
              <p class="text-sm">Regarding anonymous analytics data (Mixpanel), it is not linked to your real identity and therefore cannot be individually deleted in accordance with GDPR.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">5.4 Right to object</h3>
              <p class="mb-2">You can object to advertising tracking:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li><strong>iOS</strong>: Refuse ATT consent when requested</li>
                <li><strong>Android</strong>: Disable tracking in app settings</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">5.5 Right to data portability</h3>
              <p>The data you provide (first name, gender) is already visible and accessible in the application. Given the minimal nature of this data, we do not offer automatic export. If you wish to retrieve this data, contact us.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">5.6 Right to withdraw consent</h3>
              <p>You can withdraw your consent to advertising tracking at any time in your device settings (iOS) or application settings (Android).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 6 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">6.1 Mobile application</h3>
              <p class="mb-2">VersetVie is a <strong>native mobile application</strong> (iOS/Android) and <strong>does not use cookies</strong> (specific to the web).</p>
              <p class="mb-2">We use similar technologies to:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li>Store your preferences locally (AsyncStorage)</li>
                <li>Anonymously identify your device (Device ID)</li>
                <li>Measure application usage (analytics)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">6.2 Web version</h3>
              <p><strong>There is no web version of VersetVie</strong>. The application is available only on iOS and Android.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 7 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Protection of Minors</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <p>VersetVie is a spiritual content application accessible to all ages. However:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
              <li>We do not <strong>knowingly</strong> collect any personal data from children under 13 years old</li>
              <li>If you are a parent and notice that your child has provided personal data, contact us to have it deleted</li>
              <li>In accordance with GDPR, minors under 16 years old must obtain parental consent to use the application</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 8 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">8. Data Retention Period</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">8.1 Local data</h3>
              <p class="mb-2">Data stored on your device is retained:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Indefinitely</strong> as long as you use the application</li>
                <li><strong>Automatically deleted</strong> if you uninstall the application</li>
                <li><strong>Manually deleted</strong> if you use the "Delete my data" function</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">8.2 Analytics data</h3>
              <p>Anonymous analytics data (Mixpanel) is retained for <strong>maximum 2 years</strong> after collection, then automatically deleted.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">8.3 Attribution data</h3>
              <p>Attribution data (Tenjin) is retained for <strong>maximum 24 months</strong> after collection, in accordance with their data retention policy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 9 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">9. International Data Transfers</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">9.1 EU servers</h3>
              <p>Analytics data is stored on Mixpanel servers located in the <strong>European Union</strong> üá™üá∫, thus ensuring GDPR compliance.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">9.2 Other services</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
                <li><strong>RevenueCat</strong> (United States üá∫üá∏): Framed by Standard Contractual Clauses (SCC) to ensure a level of protection equivalent to GDPR</li>
                <li><strong>Tenjin</strong> (United States üá∫üá∏): Transfers framed by Standard Contractual Clauses and appropriate guarantees compliant with GDPR</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 10 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">10. Changes to this Policy</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <p>We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time.</p>
            <p class="mb-2">In case of substantial changes:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
              <li>You will be notified via a notification in the application</li>
              <li>The new version will be accessible in the application</li>
              <li>You will need to accept the new policy to continue using the application</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3">The last update date is indicated at the top of this document.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 11 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">11. Contact and Questions</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <p>For any questions regarding this privacy policy or to exercise your GDPR rights, you can contact us:</p>
            <p><strong>Email</strong>: <a href="mailto:privacy@versetvie.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">privacy@versetvie.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>Response time</strong>: Maximum 30 days (in accordance with GDPR)</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 12 -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">12. Supervisory Authority</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            <p>If you believe your rights are not being respected, you have the right to file a complaint with the competent supervisory authority:</p>
            <p><strong>France</strong>: Commission Nationale de l'Informatique et des Libert√©s (CNIL)</p>
            <p>Website: <a href="https://www.cnil.fr" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.cnil.fr</a></p>
            <p>Address: 3 Place de Fontenoy, 75007 Paris, France</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Conclusion -->
        <section class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-primary)]/10 to-[var(--color-secondary)]/10 border border-[var(--color-border)] text-center">
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text)] text-lg mb-2">
            <strong>Thank you for using VersetVie! üôè</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            We are committed to protecting your data and respecting your privacy.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
